@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About Us";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<div class="page-header">
    <h1>Our Story</h1>
    <p>Discover the magic behind WonderLand Adventures - where dreams come true since 1985</p>
</div>

<div class="about-container">
    <!-- 创始人部分 -->
    <div class="founder-section">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580489944761-15a19d654956" alt="Chaldear Wonder" class="founder-image">
        <div class="founder-info">
            <h2>Chaldear Wonder</h2>
            <p>Our beloved founder Chaldear Wonder was a visionary dreamer who believed in the power of joy and imagination. Born in 1945, Chaldear spent his childhood fascinated by carnivals and fairs, sketching roller coaster designs in his notebooks.</p>
            <p>After working as an engineer for 20 years, Chaldear decided to pursue his lifelong dream of creating a magical place where families could experience wonder together. He sold his house and invested all his savings to purchase the land that would become WonderLand.</p>
            <p>Chaldear personally designed the park's first five rides and could often be seen walking the grounds, chatting with guests and picking up litter until his passing in 2012. His spirit lives on in every smile at WonderLand.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 历史时间线部分 -->
    <div class="history-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our History</h2>
        <div class="history-timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-year">1985</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>The Dream Begins</h3>
                    <p>Chaldear Wonder opened the gates to WonderLand with just five rides built by hand: the Fairy Tale Carousel, Tea Cup Twirl, Mini Mine Train, Flying Elephants, and the iconic Wonder Wheel ferris wheel. The park welcomed 50,000 guests in its first year.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 其他时间线项目... -->
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 团队成员部分 -->
    <div class="team-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Meet Our Magic Makers</h2>
        <div class="team-members">
            <div class="team-member">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560250097-0b93528c311a" alt="Sarah Wonder" class="member-photo">
                <div class="member-info">
                    <h3 class="member-name">Sarah Wonder</h3>
                    <p class="member-position">Park President</p>
                    <p class="member-bio">Chaldear's daughter who grew up in the park and now leads with her father's same passion for creating magical experiences.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 其他团队成员... -->
        </div>
    </div>
</div>